## Types & Sources
- `class`: icon class name (recommended).
- `emoji`: lightweight emphasis.
- `file` / `url`: local or remote icons.
- `builtin`: built-in common icons.
- `colorful` can be declared on the component prop or on `icon.colorful`; SVG uses a currentColor mask by default and preserves original colors when colorful is true.

## API

### Props
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: icon
    type: 'ITuffIcon'
    default: '-'
    description: 'Icon object (type/value)'
